<div class="static-page">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="static-meta">Last updated: April 2025</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <p>If you create an account, we collect your email address and any profile information you provide via our authentication provider (Clerk). We use this only to save your game progress across sessions.</p>
  <p>If you play without an account, we collect no personal information.</p>

  <h2>Game saves</h2>
  <p>Authenticated users may have game progress saved server-side. This data is linked to your account and can be deleted by deleting your account.</p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>We may collect anonymous usage data (pages visited, games played) to improve the platform. This data is not linked to any individual and is not sold to third parties.</p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>We use <a href="https://clerk.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer">Clerk</a> for authentication. Clerk's privacy policy governs data processed through that service.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use session cookies required for authentication. We do not use tracking cookies.</p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>You may request deletion of your account and all associated data by contacting <a href="mailto:hello@kloopik.com">hello@kloopik.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Privacy questions: <a href="mailto:hello@kloopik.com">hello@kloopik.com</a></p>
</div>
